text: Baarle-Hertog is a municipality in the Belgian province of Antwerp. It is an Belgian exclave located in the Dutch province of North Brabant. In 2007, 2337 people lived there. It is at 51° 26 North, 04° 55 East. is noted for its complicated borders with , Netherlands. == References == Category:Municipalities of Antwerp Category:Exclaves Category:Enclaves
